---
import Single from '../layouts/Single.astro';
---
<Single
  title="Ron Bronson"
  description="Multilateral public delivery for governments at every scale."
>
  <main class="page">
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero__lede">
        <h1 class="hero__name">Ron Bronson</h1>
        <p class="hero__tagline">Multilateral public delivery</p>
      </div>
      <figure class="hero__portrait">
        <img src="/ron-bronson.jpg" alt="Ron Bronson" />
      </figure>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <p class="lede">
        I work as a forward-deployed advisor on technology and service delivery for governments.
        The practice spans federal cabinet agencies, state and local government, and international
        engagements, at the seam between policy and what reaches the people on the receiving end.
      </p>
      <p>
        Background is federal — close to a decade at 18F before independent practice — alongside
        earlier work in city and state government, and current teaching at the University of Michigan.
      </p>
      <p>
        Recent work cuts across capability assessment, delivery model design, and the trust and
        decision-engineering questions raised by AI in benefits, eligibility, and adjudication systems.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:hello@ronbronson.com">hello@ronbronson.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Writing at <a href="https://makingpublicwork.com">makingpublicwork.com</a>. Also on
        <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/ronbronson.com">Bluesky</a>,
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ronbronson/">LinkedIn</a>, and
        <a href="https://github.com/quarterback">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Single>


